{"tid":2170682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"爆大鑊1〡 張子強頭馬出冊 鎖在小木箱10日 郭炳湘靠紅顏奔波救人 ： 畀足錢我哋點會虐待佢 (壹週刊","createTime":"2020-08-23T12:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T12:17:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea53234c36e324bf0fd67eec091ed7de66d3f83f","tid":2170682,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"#張子強 #郭炳湘 #李澤鉅<br />\n<br />\n爆大鑊1〡<br />\n張子強頭馬出冊 鎖在小木箱10日 郭炳湘靠紅顏奔波救人 ：<br />\n畀足錢我哋點會虐待佢<br />\n(壹週刊 Next)<br />\n20200822<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9Yf76AUbDBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9Yf76AUbDBY&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=3cc53393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9Yf76AUbDBY</a><br />\n<br />\n壹週刊 NEXT<br />\n573K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n1998年12月6日，大賊張子強在內地被捕遭槍決。而當年與張子強一起策劃綁架李澤鉅、郭炳湘的劉鼎勳，則被判無期徒刑，因在監獄行為良好，於2015年4月16日被釋放。今日，劉鼎勳接受老友陳慎芝訪問，講述當年做案經過。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_6727...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_6727...&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=2802fd53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_6727...&h=758d1ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_6727...</a>"},{"pid":"9f1ab8be1f18d421156207293ec3f76ad0e167fb","tid":2170682,"uid":252142,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}